    {
      "index": 206,
      "style": "Heading 1",
      "text": "部署指南"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "style": "Heading 2",
      "text": "环境要求"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "style": "Heading 2",
      "text": "后端部署"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "步骤1：构建项目"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "# 进入后端项目目录\ncd career-planning-backend\n\n# 使用 Maven 构建\nmvn clean package -DskipTests\n\n# 构建产物位于 target/ 目录下"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "步骤2：配置应用"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "# 编辑 application.properties 配置文件\n# 设置数据库连接、Redis、RabbitMQ、JWT密钥、AI服务地址等\n\n# 关键配置项：\nspring.datasource.url=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/career_backend\nspring.data.redis.host=localhost\nspring.rabbitmq.host=localhost\njwt.secret=your_jwt_secret_key\nai.service.url=http://localhost:9000"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "步骤3：启动服务"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "# 方式一：直接运行\njava -jar target/career-planning-backend-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar\n\n# 方式二：使用 Maven 运行（开发环境）\nmvn spring-boot:run\n\n# 方式三：使用 systemd 管理（生产环境）\nsudo systemctl enable career-backend\nsudo systemctl start career-backend"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "style": "Heading 2",
      "text": "前端部署"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "步骤1：安装依赖并构建"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "# 进入前端项目目录\ncd career-planning-frontend\n\n# 安装依赖\nnpm install\n\n# 配置生产环境变量\n# 编辑 .env.production 设置 API 地址\nVITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.your-domain.com\n\n# 构建生产版本\nnpm run build"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "步骤2：配置 Nginx"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "server {\n    listen 80;\n    server_name www.your-domain.com;\n    return 301 https://$server_name$request_uri;\n}\n\nserver {\n    listen 443 ssl http2;\n    server_name www.your-domain.com;\n\n    ssl_certificate /etc/letsencrypt/live/your-domain.com/fullchain.pem;\n    ssl_certificate_key /etc/letsencrypt/live/your-domain.com/privkey.pem;\n\n    root /var/www/career-frontend/dist;\n    index index.html;\n\n    # SPA 路由支持\n    location / {\n        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;\n    }\n\n    # API 代理\n    location /api/ {\n        proxy_pass http://localhost:8080;\n        proxy_set_header Host $host;\n        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n    }\n}"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "步骤3：部署静态文件"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "# 复制构建产物\nsudo mkdir -p /var/www/career-frontend\nsudo cp -r dist/* /var/www/career-frontend/\n\n# 设置权限\nsudo chown -R nginx:nginx /var/www/career-frontend\n\n# 重载 Nginx\nsudo nginx -t\nsudo systemctl reload nginx"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "style": "Heading 1",
      "text": "结语"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "\"职引未来——基于AI的大学生职业规划智能体系统\"以\"大模型+微服务\"架构重构了大学生职业规划的全链路服务流程，通过AI智能体中枢（职业规划师、简历优化师、面试官等）破解了职业规划服务中的个性化难题，结合智能简历系统、AI面试官、职位匹配分析等创新功能实现了从自我认知到就业准备的全流程覆盖。"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "系统采用前后端分离的微服务架构，后端基于Spring Boot 3.5.9构建，AI服务基于FastAPI + Python构建，前端采用Vue 3 + TypeScript + Element Plus。通过整合多种AI技术和业务模块，系统为大学生提供了全方位、个性化的职业发展支持平台。"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "未来，系统将继续依托AI技术的持续升级，拓展更多职业发展场景，如实习推荐、行业分析、技能提升计划等，推动大学生职业规划服务的智能化转型，构建安全可信的智能职业发展生态。"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "职引未来开发组"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "2026年04月13日"
    }
  ],
